Logistic equations

A simple model

\[N_{i+1} - N_{i} = \Delta_{i}N = \frac{rN_{i}(K-N_{i})}{K}\]

\[N_{i + 1} = N{i} + \Delta_{i}N\]

\[N_{0} = 1\]

\[r = 1/20\]

\[K = 20\]

\[\frac{dN}{dt} = \frac{rN(K-N)}{K}\]

delta.logis.eq <- function(N,r,K) r*N*(K-N) / K

r <- 1/20
K <- 20
N0 <- 1

Res <- data.frame(time = 0, abundance = N0)
N <- N0
for(i in 1:200){
  Ni <- N + delta.logis.eq(N = N,r = r, K = K)
  Res <- rbind(Res,c(i,Ni))
  N <- Ni
}

1 dimension bi-stability

Function

\[\frac{dA}{dt} = f(A) - \gamma A\]

\[f(A) = K(\alpha + (1-\alpha)\frac{A^{n}}{A{n}+K^{n}_{D}})\]

bistability <- function(t,y,params){
  K <- parms[1]
  alpha <- parms[2]
  n <- params[3]
  KD <- params[4]
  gamma <- params[5]
  
  A <- y[1]
  
  fA <- K*(alpha + (1-alpha)*(A^n)/(A^n+KD^n))
  diffA <- fA - gamma*A
  
  res <- list(x = c(diffA))
  
  return(res)
}

#params
parms <- c(K = 0.16,
           alpha = 0.25,
           n = 6,
           KD = 45,
           gamma = 0.002)

#' Scan starting values
x0_scan <- function(A,times = 0:5000, func = bistability){
  Res <- NULL
  for(i in A){
    x0 <- i
    res <- lsode(y = x0,times = times,func = func, parms = parms)
    res <- as.data.frame(res)
    res$A0 <- i
    Res <- rbind(Res,res)
  }
  return(Res)
}

#Set starting values
Res <- x0_scan(A = seq(10,100,by = 5))

Res.time <- melt(data = Res,id.vars = c("time","A0"),variable.name = "species",value.name = "abundance")
Res.time$A0 <- factor(Res.time$A0)
p1 <- ggplot(subset(Res.time,A0 %in% c(35,60)),aes(x = time, y = abundance)) +
  facet_wrap(~A0) +
  geom_line(aes(color = species),size = 3,alpha = 0.5) +
  ylim(c(10,max(Res.time$abundance))) +
  theme_classic() +
  theme(axis.title = element_text(size = 16, face = "bold"),
        axis.text = element_text(size = 12, angle = 90))
p1

ggsave("bistability_example.png",p1,width = 5,height = 4)

p1 <- ggplot(Res.time,aes(x = time, y = abundance)) +
  geom_line(aes(color = A0),size = 3,alpha = 0.5) +
  scale_color_discrete(guide = guide_legend(ncol = 2)) +
  ylim(c(10,max(Res.time$abundance))) +
  theme_classic() +

Lotka-Volterra competition

Model:

\[\frac{dA}{dt} = A(r_A - K_AA - aB)\]

\[\frac{dB}{dt} = B(r_B - K_BB - bA)\]

lotka.volterra.competition <- function(t,y,params){
  rA <- parms[1]
  rB <- params[2]
  KA <- params[3]
  KB <- params[4]
  cA <- params[5]
  cB <- params[6]
  A <- y[1]
  B <- y[2]
  
  diffA <- A*(rA - KA*A - cA*B)
  diffB <- B*(rB - KB*B - cB*A)
  
  res <- list(x = c(diffA,diffB))
  
  return(res)
}

# parameters
parms <- c(rA = 4, 
           rB = 2,
           KA = 3,
           KB = 2,
           cA = 2,
           cB = 1)

Res <- NULL
# Try different starting positoon
x0 <- c(A = 3 , B = 0.4)
res <- lsode(y = x0,times = 0:50,func = lotka.volterra.competition, parms = parms)
res <- as.data.frame(res)
res$case <- "case1"
Res <- rbind(Res,res)

x0 <- c(A = 0.2 , B = 0.4)
res <- lsode(y = x0,times = 0:50,func = lotka.volterra.competition, parms = parms)
res <- as.data.frame(res)
res$case <- "case2"
Res <- rbind(Res,res)

x0 <- c(A = 0.2 , B = 2)
res <- lsode(y = x0,times = 0:50,func = lotka.volterra.competition, parms = parms)
res <- as.data.frame(res)
res$case <- "case3"
Res <- rbind(Res,res)

x0 <- c(A = 3 , B = 2)
res <- lsode(y = x0,times = 0:50,func = lotka.volterra.competition, parms = parms)
res <- as.data.frame(res)
res$case <- "case4"
Res <- rbind(Res,res)

Res.time <- melt(data = Res,id.vars = c("time","case"),variable.name = "species",value.name = "abundance")

p1 <- ggplot(Res.time,aes(x = time, y = abundance)) +
  facet_wrap(~case) +
  geom_line(aes(color = species),size = 3,alpha = 0.5) +
  ylim(c(0,max(Res.time$abundance))) +
  theme_classic() +
  theme(axis.title = element_text(size = 16, face = "bold"),
        axis.text = element_text(size = 12))
p1

ggsave("LVcompetition.png",p1,width = 5,height = 4)

p1 <- ggplot(Res,aes(x = A, y = B)) +

Lotka volterra predator-prey

Model, should be equivalent to the other

\[\frac{dA}{dt} = \alpha A - \beta AB\]

\[\frac{dB}{dt} = \delta AB - \gamma B\]

lotka.volterra.predatorprey <- function(t,y,params){
  alpha <- parms[1]
  beta <- params[2]
  delta <- params[3]
  gamma <- params[4]
  A <- y[1]
  B <- y[2]
  
  diffA <- alpha*A - beta*A*B
  diffB <- delta*A*B - gamma*B
  
  res <- list(x = c(diffA,diffB))
  
  return(res)
}

# Starting conditions


Res <- NULL
# Case 1
x0 <- c(A = 80, B = 40)
parms <- c(alpha = 1/5, 
           beta = 1/200, delta = 1/300,
           gamma = 1/5)
res <- lsode(y = x0,times = 0:200,func = lotka.volterra.predatorprey, parms = parms)
res <- as.data.frame(res)
res$case <- "Case 1"
Res <- rbind(Res,res)

#Case 2
x0 <- c(A = 80, B = 40)
parms <- c(alpha = 2/3, 
           beta = 4/3, delta = 1,
           gamma = 1)
res <- lsode(y = x0,times = 0:200,func = lotka.volterra.predatorprey, parms = parms)
res <- as.data.frame(res)
res$case <- "Case 2"
Res <- rbind(Res,res)

Res.time <- melt(data = Res,id.vars = c("time","case"),variable.name = "species",value.name = "abundance")

p1 <- ggplot(Res.time,aes(x = time, y = abundance)) +
  facet_wrap(~case) +
  geom_line(aes(color = species),size = 3,alpha = 0.5) +
  theme_classic() +
  theme(axis.title = element_text(size = 16, face = "bold"),
        axis.text = element_text(size = 12))
p1

p1 <- ggplot(Res,aes(x = A, y = B)) +

  geom_path(aes(color = case),size = 3,alpha = 0.5) +
  theme_classic() +

        axis.text = element_text(size = 12))
